dplyr verbs
df |&gt;
  filter(age &gt;= 18) |&gt;
  select(id, age, sbp) |&gt;
  mutate(sbp_z = (sbp - mean(sbp)) / sd(sbp)) |&gt;
  group_by(arm) |&gt;
  summarise(mean_sbp = mean(sbp, na.rm = TRUE), n = n())
Joins: left_join, inner_join, anti_join by a key.
Missingness: is.na(), drop_na(), tidyr::complete().

